}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c2XKCaH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2XKCaH.jpg&h=c9d4040b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵一搵個名同深水埗警署, 發現到原來阿sir係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Commander Mr. Sa Yung  San, Chesley</strong></span></span><br />\n <br />\n搵一搵相, 個樣又真係match架wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Ynq56w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ynq56w.jpg&h=7f7ff910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲上過香港01添! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCRfJUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgCRfJUD.jpg&h=c842abfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來10年前黎香港係為左做黑警濫權扑野, 果然有大志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fsL0U1J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfsL0U1J.jpg&h=e5b696d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人睇到佢no. 可以向狗署投訴呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mgwWtnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmgwWtnL.jpg&h=097f9f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hT6SL9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhT6SL9p.jpg&h=930550d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>同場加映</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n阿sir講比大家知警犬點諗呢場運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0E5cMbq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0E5cMbq.jpg&h=625dd7c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JoPhcRw.jpg\" data